<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>French (Français) and Spanish (Español) translations are now available in Foundry's language picker, so you
        can run Calendaria in those locales</li>
      <li>The countup enricher can now point at a calendar note by name, or auto-resolve to its own event's date when
        embedded on a note page, so you no longer have to hardcode the target date</li>
      <li>Today's date is now visibly highlighted in MiniCal and BigCal with a distinct background tint and day-number
        colour, and the bundled theme presets were recoloured so the today accent stays readable when also selected</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Ambient weather audio now fades out when your token enters a Foundry region with the core Suppress Weather
        behavior, and restores when you leave, so indoor and sheltered areas stay quiet without manual muting</li>
      <li>Cinematic event cards now stay in sync with the day shown on the clock and respect note permissions, so cards
        no longer bleed into the following day and players no longer glimpse hidden GM notes</li>
    </ul>

  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
